The '''Ebon Sea''' was the one of the few bodies of water on [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]]. It was a stagnant sea covered in scum, and had been contaminated by seepage from [[Golbah's Pit]].

The land around the Ebon Sea was populated by [[Acklay/Legends|acklays]] that had bred there after escaping from captivity. Amphibious [[mutant acklay]]s lived beneath its waters, surfacing to attack prey on the land. [[Geonosian hydra]]s lived on the muddy sea bottom.

